Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
