Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
