Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:42.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:48.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
