Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:26.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:29.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:34.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
